Overview
========

packdude is a small package manager inspired by Pacman (https://www.archlinux.org/pacman/) and PPM (http://bkhome.org/woof/ppm.htm).

It's under heavy development, in its early stages.

Dependencies
============

packdude depends on:
  - libarchive (http://libarchive.org/) with LZMA2 (http://tukaani.org/xz/) support
  - zlib (http://zlib.net/)
  - libcurl (http://curl.haxx.se/)

Planned Features
================
  - Support for a single architecture
  - Package download
  - Package updates
  - A createrepo-like tool

